<div style="background:#1cb403; width: 800px; image-rendering: auto"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/corruption/gradientstart.png" width="800px" alt="gradientstart.png" class="image" /><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/corruption/CORE_OPEN.png" width="200px" alt="CORE_OPEN.png" class="image" /></div>
